Package: openattic
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-base,
 openattic-module-lvm
Suggests: python-django-rosetta
Description: Comprehensive storage management system
 Meta Package that installs the most common set of openATTIC modules along
 with the basic requirements.

Package: openattic-base
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${python:Depends},
 python-django,
 dbus,
 python-dbus,
 python-m2crypto,
 python-django-extdirect (>= 0.6),
 python-statgrab,
 libjs-extjs (>= 3.0.0), libjs-extjs (<< 4.0)
Recommends: libapache2-mod-wsgi
Description: Basic requirements for openATTIC.
 Installs the basic set of dependencies required to run
 openATTIC, namely the web GUI, RPCd and Systemd.

Package: openattic-module-lvm
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-base,
 lvm2, parted, ntfs-3g
Description: LVM module for openATTIC.
 Installs the LVM module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-nfs
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-module-lvm,
 nfs-kernel-server
Description: NFS module for openATTIC.
 Installs the NFS module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-iet-iscsi
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-module-lvm,
 iscsitarget, iscsitarget-dkms
Description: IET iSCSI module for openATTIC.
 Installs the IET iSCSI module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-samba
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-module-lvm, samba
Description: Samba module for openATTIC.
 Installs the Samba module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-ftp
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-module-lvm,
