Description: FTP module for openATTIC.
 Installs the FTP module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-munin
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-base,
 munin-node, munin
Description: Munin module for openATTIC.
 Installs the Munin module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-drbd
Architecture: all
Depends: openattic-module-lvm,
 drbd8-utils
Description: DRBD module for openATTIC.
 Installs the DRBD module for openATTIC.

Package: openattic-module-http
